## Run auth.http → Login first to populate {{token}}

###
## ─── Browse Shops ───
###

### Browse Thornhaven General Store (must be at 50,50)
GET {{host}}/shops/thornhaven
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Browse Ironpeak Forge (must be at 74,71)
GET {{host}}/shops/ironpeak
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Browse Tidecrest Trading Post (must be at 3,46)
GET {{host}}/shops/tidecrest
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Browse Pearlshore Curio Shop (must be at 91,73)
GET {{host}}/shops/pearlshore
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Browse Mosswood Apothecary (must be at 80,48)
GET {{host}}/shops/mosswood
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
## ─── Buy Items ───
###

### Buy a health potion from Thornhaven
POST {{host}}/shops/thornhaven/buy
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "itemId": "health-potion",
  "quantity": 2
}

### Buy a leather armor from Thornhaven
POST {{host}}/shops/thornhaven/buy
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "itemId": "leather-armor"
}

### Buy a steel longsword from Stormwatch
POST {{host}}/shops/stormwatch/buy
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "itemId": "steel-longsword"
}

###
## ─── Sell Items ───
###

### Sell a health potion at Thornhaven
POST {{host}}/shops/thornhaven/sell
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "itemId": "health-potion",
  "quantity": 1
}

### Sell a copper dagger at Thornhaven
POST {{host}}/shops/thornhaven/sell
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "itemId": "copper-dagger"
}

###
## ─── Error Cases ───
###

### Try to browse a shop you're not at — should fail (400)
GET {{host}}/shops/ironpeak
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Try to buy an item not in this shop — should fail (400)
POST {{host}}/shops/thornhaven/buy
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "itemId": "plate-armor"
}

### Try to buy with insufficient gold — should fail (400)
POST {{host}}/shops/thornhaven/buy
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "itemId": "iron-longsword",
  "quantity": 99
}

### Try to sell a quest item — should fail (400)
POST {{host}}/shops/thornhaven/sell
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "itemId": "ancient-relic"
}

### Try to sell an item you don't have — should fail (400)
POST {{host}}/shops/thornhaven/sell
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "itemId": "steel-greatsword"
}

### Try to shop while traveling — should fail (409 Conflict)
GET {{host}}/shops/thornhaven
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Try to shop while resting — should fail (409 Conflict)
GET {{host}}/shops/thornhaven
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Try to browse a non-existent shop — should fail (404)
GET {{host}}/shops/nonexistent-town
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
